snippet.title: OMNO Gameplay footage
snippet.description:
Kickstarter http://kickstarter.playomno.com 
Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/969760/Omno/
OMNO, developed by solo indie dev Jonas Manke, is an atmospheric adventure about a journey of discovery through an ancient world of wonders. 


Omno is a single player adventure game made in Unreal Engine that will take you through lush forests, across a sun blasted desert, over a frigid tundra, and where the power of a lost civilisation will even carry you to the clouds. On the way you will meet strange creatures, encounter many surprises and maybe make a friend in 3D puzzle platformer style.

Omo is developed by Jonas Manke (aka Studio Inkyfox) and coming to Steam in 2019. 

Find out more about Omno:

Website: http://www.playomno.com/
Kickstarter: http://kickstarter.playomno.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/StudioInkyfox
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/OmnoGame/
Discord: https://discordapp.com/invite/2BAkYky
